The paper discusses the rendering process used in animation, which falls under computer graphics (cs.GR) and cloud computing (cs.CE). The paper also discusses the taxonomy and classification of rendering services, which could fall under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
